  <brief_title>A Study to Investigate the Safety and Effectiveness of Aspheric Laser Refractive Surgery Treatments for Myopia</brief_title>
  <official_title>Compare the Safety and Effectiveness of Two Versions of the Bausch &amp; Lomb Zyoptix™ Tissue Saving Aspheric Algorithm to the Current Zyoptix™ Tissue Saving Algorithm When Used for Myopia and Myopic Astigmatism Lasik Treatment</official_title>
  <sponsors>
