  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this study was to compare the safety and effectiveness of two versions of
      the Bausch &amp; Lomb Zyoptix Tissue Saving Aspheric Algorithm versus the current Zyoptix Tissue
      Saving Algorithm when used for myopia and myopic astigmatism LASIK treatment.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
